title: Carpentry & Woodworking
description:
Description
Now you can start an adventure of doing-it-yourself that will bring a lifetime of pleasure in working with your hands and pride in your finished projects. This book teaches the basic skills and offers 20 projects to put those new skills to work.Learn to choose and use the right woods and tools for any job, from building fine furniture to building a house. With these materials, you will discover how to make basic wood joints, use the correct fasteners to hold projects together, and how to sand and finish any kind of wood surface
